00:26:56.380 --> 00:26:58.750
to make any excuses about it.

00:26:58.750 --> 00:27:01.570
So, I don't know, that's probably,

00:27:01.570 --> 00:27:04.210
that's my own personal
kind of love and challenge.

00:27:04.210 --> 00:27:07.580
Other is kind of to try
to find the instrument

00:27:07.580 --> 00:27:11.340
and find the places that,
the way that it sings.

00:27:11.340 --> 00:27:13.620
You know, you try to find
the soul of the instrument,

00:27:13.620 --> 00:27:16.560
and you have usually a little
bit of time to do that.

00:27:16.560 --> 00:27:21.680
And then, I think once you find
that, I think it's easy to find,

00:27:21.680 --> 00:27:25.690
I think any musician has to find
