have that, and you can kind

00:27:28.600 --> 00:27:36.690 position:56%
of fit your sound around your
place, and so I think that's always,

00:27:36.690 --> 00:27:38.560
I start with myself and
the piano sound first,

00:27:38.560 --> 00:27:42.440
and then I think once I, then
I feel like I can open up.

00:27:42.440 --> 00:27:46.970
But I think if I didn't do the,
if I didn't have that first,

00:27:46.970 --> 00:27:49.870
